name: Tish James
tweet: New York has some of the country’s toughest gun laws, but too many guns are illegally trafficked from other states and our communities pay the price.   From gun trafficking takedowns to buybacks we will continue to use the power of this office to save lives.  https://t.co/8YMEifsjgX

name: Tish James
tweet: People often ask me, “Why do you call yourself the People’s Lawyer?”   My answer? Because my job is to protect the people of New York, and ensure their needs are met at every level. I serve the people of New York by any means necessary.

name: Tish James
tweet: Let’s agree to make history, to break ground, and build a more fair society as we recover from this pandemic.  There is no upstate or downstate way to make government work, but we must ensure better outcomes for the people of NY. The status quo won’t do.
